description.oldValue:
Users
will be able to enroll their face and create a face profile using the new
enrollment process in the Teams desktop client. The face profile is used in
Teams Rooms meetings where an Intelligent Camera capable of People Recognition
is deployed to recognize in-room attendees, and then labels their identity for
all meeting participants, both in-room and remote.
